(30, 20, 'FULL STACK IN PHP', ' مطور مواقع إلكترونية PHP', '<div><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;=\"\" display:=\"\" inline=\"\" !important;\"=\"\"><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">A Full Stack developer is responsible for front and back-end web development. Usually, good full stack developers will understand several how to work with several languages and databases including PHP, HTML, CSS, JavaScript and everything in between. Writing a good job description for a full stack developer will require you to understand the skills and responsibilities needed for the specific project and ongoing work.Below you’ll find a sample template job description for a full stack developer. You can copy the Full Stack Developer job description, but make sure to add your own information for company culture, perks/benefits, as well as double-check that the skills match your exact requirements.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\"></p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">Below you’ll find a sample template job description for an Android developer. You can copy the Android developer job description, but make sure to add your own information for company culture, perks/benefits, as well as double-check that the skills match your exact requirements.</p></span></div>', '<div><span style=\"color: rgb(41, 48, 59); font-size: 0.9em; display: inline !important;\">فى هذا الكورس ستتعلم برمجة و تصميم المواقع من خلال تعلم بعض اللغات و التقنيات الخاصه بهم مثل</span><br></div><div><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10.5px; margin-left: 0px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(41, 48, 59); font-family: \" open=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 15px;\"=\"\">HTML, CSS, Javascript, JQuery, Bootstrap, PHP, MySQLi, AJAX</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10.5px; margin-left: 0px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(41, 48, 59); font-family: \" open=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 15px;\"=\"\">بالأضافة الى عدد من الأمثلة العملية&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10.5px; margin-left: 0px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(41, 48, 59); font-family: \" open=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 15px;\"=\"\">بعد الأنتهاء من الكورس ستتمكن من انشاء موقع إليكتروني بشكل كامل لشركة أو مصنع أو غيرهم و العمل من خلال منصات العمل الحر و شركات تصميم المواقع</p></div>', '<ul class=\"what-you-get__items\" style=\"list-style: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10.5px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; justify-content: space-between; flex-wrap: wrap; color: rgb(41, 48, 59); font-family: \" open=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 15px;=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgb(249,=\"\" 249,=\"\" 249);\"=\"\"><li class=\"what-you-get__item what-you-get__item--columns\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 10px; width: 323.094px;\"><span class=\"what-you-get__text\">Learn Web Development from Scratch - Frontend &amp; Backend (Beginner to Advanced)</span></li><li class=\"what-you-get__item what-you-get__item--columns\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 10px; width: 323.094px;\"><span class=\"what-you-get__text\"><span style=\"color: inherit; font-family: inherit; display: inline !important;\">Learn Javascript (Arrays, Functions, Objects, Events and much more..)</span></span></li><li class=\"what-you-get__item what-you-get__item--columns\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 10px; width: 323.094px;\"><span class=\"what-you-get__text\"><span style=\"color: inherit; font-family: inherit; display: inline !important;\">Learn HTML 5 and CSS 3 from Scratch (Beginner to Advanced)</span></span></li><li class=\"what-you-get__item what-you-get__item--columns\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 10px; width: 323.094px;\"><span class=\"what-you-get__text\"><span style=\"display: inline !important;\">Create a Resume Template with HTML5 and CSS3</span></span></li><li class=\"what-you-get__item what-you-get__item--columns\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 10px; width: 323.094px;\"><span class=\"what-you-get__text\"><span style=\"display: inline !important;\">Learn Complete Front End Development</span></span></li><li class=\"what-you-get__item what-you-get__item--columns\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 10px; width: 323.094px;\"><span class=\"what-you-get__text\"><span style=\"display: inline !important;\">Learn Document Object Model (DOM) in Javascript - Advanced</span></span></li><li class=\"what-you-get__item what-you-get__item--columns\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 10px; width: 323.094px;\"><span class=\"what-you-get__text\"><span style=\"display: inline !important;\">Learn Twitter Bootstrap 4.0 (Beginner to Advanced)</span></span></li><li class=\"what-you-get__item what-you-get__item--columns\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 10px; width: 323.094px;\"><span class=\"what-you-get__text\"><span style=\"display: inline !important;\">Learn Complete Backend End Development</span></span></li><li class=\"what-you-get__item what-you-get__item--columns\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 10px; width: 323.094px;\"><span class=\"what-you-get__text\"><span style=\"display: inline !important;\">Learn the Fundamental of PHP and Mysql</span></span></li><li class=\"what-you-get__item what-you-get__item--columns\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 10px; width: 323.094px;\"><span class=\"what-you-get__text\"><span style=\"display: inline !important;\">Learn and Apply Media Queries and The Responsive Web Design - To Build Mobile Websites</span></span></li><li class=\"what-you-get__item what-you-get__item--columns\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 10px; width: 323.094px;\"><span class=\"what-you-get__text\"><span style=\"display: inline !important;\">Learn Database Design and Modeling in Mysql Server (Beginner to Advanced)</span></span></li></ul>', '<p style=\"margin: 6px 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-size: 14px; text-align: right;\"><br>• عمل تصميم جذاب لموقعك.<br>• برمجة مواقع الكترونية بمهنية عالية.<br>• كيفية وضع موقعك على قائمة أصدقاء محركات البحث SEO.<br>• تأمين وحماية الموقع.<br>• كيفية العمل عبر الانترنت والربح من تصميم وبرمجة الويب وتطبيقاته.<br>تنقسم الدورة إلى قسمين رئيسيين :</p><p style=\"margin: 6px 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-size: 14px; text-align: right;\">أولاً : Front–end development</p><p style=\"margin: 6px 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-size: 14px; text-align: right;\">• بناء هيكلية المواقع باستخدام HTML5<br>• بناء واجهات المواقع بـ CSS3<br>• عمل تأثيرات على الموقع باستخدام Javascript<br>• استخدام المكتبات الجاهزة في jQuery لبناء عناصر متقدمة أكثر<br>• التعامل مع إطار العمل Bootstrap لإنشاء موقع بتصميم تفاعلي متين.<br>• تعلم كيف تحدث محتويات موقعك باستخدام AJAX دون الحاجة لإعادة تحميلها.<br>ثانياً : Back–end development</p><p style=\"margin: 6px 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-size: 14px; text-align: right;\">• بناء كود قوي للموقع بطريقة منظمة باستخدام PHP<br>• ربط قواعد البيانات بالموقع PHP and MySQL with MySQLi<br>• التعامل مع عناصر البيانات MySQL with PDO<br>• التعامل مع دوال JSON<br>• استخدام المصفوفات Arrays<br>• برمجة نظام الجلسة باستخدام Sessions<br>• جمع المعلومات للموقع بواسطة Cookies<br>• استخدام المكتبات بشكل فعال Application Libraries<br>• التعامل مع خرائط جوجل Google Map API<br><span style=\"display: inline !important;\">&nbsp;</span><br></p>', '1', 30, '1556189539-PHPFULLSTACK.jpg', '200', '50', '<font color=\"#000000\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; display: inline !important;\">FrontEnd Engineer Course :&nbsp;</span><span class=\"text_exposed_show\" style=\"display: inline; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><br><span class=\"_5mfr\" style=\"margin: 0px 1px; font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"_6qdm\" style=\"background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: contain; text-shadow: none; vertical-align: text-bottom; font-family: inherit; height: 16px; width: 16px; font-size: 16px; background-image: url(\" \");\"=\"\" https:=\"\" static.xx.fbcdn.net=\"\" images=\"\" emoji.php=\"\" v9=\"\" t8d=\"\" 1=\"\" 16=\"\" 2611.png?_nc_eui2=\"AeGeogbDJbdBoyD_Ve0CpKlSyHp3j9aC0OYpmygKP6PeO8iO-1MYXDvElMc2_LccIeK-UL5E8QOyruEQhw-xNj4dkFXMAbw72qQogzMXZgP4FQ\" );\"\"=\"\">☑️</span></span>&nbsp;HTML / HTML5 : HTML&nbsp;<span style=\"\" open=\"\" sans\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;=\"\" display:=\"\" inline=\"\" !important;\"=\"\">stands for&nbsp;</span><em style=\"\" open=\"\" sans\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;\"=\"\">Hyper Text Markup Language,&nbsp;</em><span style=\"\" open=\"\" sans\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;=\"\" display:=\"\" inline=\"\" !important;\"=\"\">which is used to create web pages.&nbsp;It is one of the most powerful languages to create a&nbsp;website and very simple to learn. The HTML elements are represented by&nbsp;</span><em style=\"\" open=\"\" sans\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;\"=\"\">Tags</em><span style=\"\" open=\"\" sans\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;=\"\" display:=\"\" inline=\"\"