tion requirements.</span><br open=\"\" sans\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;\"=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33);\">- SQL Server&nbsp;<br>- Ajax Request :&nbsp;</span><span open=\"\" sans\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" display:=\"\" inline=\"\" !important;\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33);\">Asynchronous JavaScript And XML (AJAX) is a technique for creating better, faster, and more interactive web applications with the help of XML, HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.</span><br></p><span class=\"text_exposed_show\" style=\"display: inline; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-size: 14px;\"></span>', '1970-01-01', '1970-01-01', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(32, 20, 'FULL STACK IN PYTHON', 'الدورة الشاملة في ال PYTHON', '<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">Python programming language was developed by Python Software Foundation to emphasize on code readability as it allows programmers to express concepts in fewer lines of code providing them with constructs that enable clear programming on both small and large scales.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">This course aims to provide trainees with an overview of how to build web and database applications and interactive web maps and create working Python scripts, trainees will learn the Object-Oriented Programming (OOP) in Python, as this course covers the following topics: Basics of Python, OOP using Python, HTML, CSS and Bootstrap, JS and JQuery, and Database.</p>', '<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">تعتبر لغة البرمجة بايثون Python أحد أشهر لغات البرمجة القوية مفتوحة المصدر القابلة للتطوير والتي تعمل علي كل أنظمة التشغيل وتتكامل مع غيرها من اللغات بحيث تتميز ببساطة كتابتها وقراءتها حيث أنها تتطلب من المبرمجين عدداً أقل من أسطر الكودات باحتواءها على تنظيمات وبنيات تسمح بالبرمجة بشكل واضح على كل المقاييس الكبيرة</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">والصغيرة. تستخدم هذه اللغة في برمجة المواقع الإلكترونية, وتعتبر من أكثر اللغات المطلوبة في الوطن العربي وأوروبا وأميركا في الآونة الأخيرة, كما تصنف رواتب المبرمجين العاملين بلغة Python من أعلى الرواتب عالمياً.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">تهدف هذه الدورة إلى تزويد المتدربين بنظرة عامة عن كيفية إنشاء تطبيقات الويب وقاعدة البيانات وخرائط الويب التفاعلية بالإضافة إلى كتابة كودات ونصوص البايثون، سيتعرف المتدربون من خلال هذه الدورة على البرمجة كائنية التوجه OOP باستخدام لغة بايثون بالإضافة إلى التعرف بلغة Python, مجالات استخدام لغة Python, بناء المواقع باستخدام لغة Python. بحيث تغطي الدورة المواضيع التالية: لغة ترميز النص الفائق HTML, CSS, Bootstrap, JS, JQuery, وقواعد البيانات Database</p>', '<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">Introducing trainees to Python programming language.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">Understanding how to build web and database applications.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">Learning to create interactive web maps and working Python scripts.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">Understanding the Object-Oriented Programming (OOP) in Python, Django Framework, URLs, and Views.</p>', '<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">تعريف المتدربين على لغة برمجة بايثون.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">فهم كيفية إنشاء تطبيقات الويب وقاعدة البيانات.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">دراسة كيفية بناء خرائط الويب التفاعلية بالإضافة إلى كتابة كودات ونصوص البايثون.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">التعرف على البرمجة كائنية التوجه OOP باستخدام لغة بايثون, إطار عمل ويب Django، عناوين الإنترنت URL, وكذلك المشاهدات Views.</p>', '1', 30, '1556185324-PYTHONFULLSTACK.jpg', '200', '50', '<div><span class=\"text_exposed_show\" style=\"display: inline; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-size: 14px;\"><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">FrontEnd Engineer Course :</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">☑️ HTML / HTML5 : HTML stands for Hyper Text Markup Language, which is used to create web pages. It is one of the most powerful languages to create a website and very simple to</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">learn. The HTML elements are represented by Tags. Those tags are rendered as Page Content on the website.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">☑️CSS / CSS3 : CSS stands for Cascading Style Sheet. It will add look and styles to the HTML tags and as a result, the site looks and feels good. We cannot do styling with HTML tags; this is why we have to use CSS.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">☑️ Bootstrap : It\'s a framework which is used for designing a website or web page. It contains HTML and CSS based design templates.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">☑️ JQuery : is a collection of JavaScript library functions. It is also open source and mostly it is designed to simplify the client-side scripting of HTML. The main purpose of jQuery is to provide an easy way to use JavaScript on websites to make them more interactive and attractive.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\"></p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">BackEnd Devloper:</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">- python object and data structure basics</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">- Python comparison operators</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">- python statments</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">- methods and functions</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">- object oriented programming</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">- Django Framework : Django Installation &amp; Configurations</p></span></div>', '<p style=\"font-size: medium; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">FrontEnd Engineer Course :</p><p style=\"font-size: medium; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">☑️ HTML / HTML5 : HTML stands for Hyper Text Markup Language, which is used to create web pages. It is one of the most powerful languages to create a website and very simple to</p><p style=\"font-size: medium; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">learn. The HTML elements are represented by Tags. Those tags are rendered as Page Content on the website.</p><p style=\"font-size: medium; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">☑️CSS / CSS3 : CSS stands for Cascading Style Sheet. It will add look and styles to the HTML tags and as a result, the site looks and feels good. We cannot do styling with HTML tags; this is why we have to use CSS.</p><p style=\"font-size: medium; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">☑️ Bootstrap : It\'s a framework which is used for designing a website or web page. It contains HTML and CSS based design templates.</p><p style=\"font-size: medium; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">☑️ JQuery : is a collection of JavaScript library functions. It is also open source and mostly it is designed to simplify the client-side scripting of HTML. The main purpose of jQuery is to provide an easy way to use JavaScript on websites to make them more interactive and attractive.</p><p style=\"font-size: medium; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\"></p><p style=\"font-size: medium; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">BackEnd Devloper:</p><p style=\"font-size: medium; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">- python object and data structure basics</p><p style=\"font-size: medium; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">- Python comparison operators</p><p style=\"font-size: medium; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">- python statments</p><p style=\"font-size: medium; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">- methods and functions</p><p style=\"font-size: medium; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">- object oriented programming</p><p style=\"font-size: medium; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">- Django Framework : Django Installation &amp; Configurations</p>', '1970-01-01', '1970-01-01', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(33, 20, 'FULL STACK IN ANDROID', ' الدورة الشاملة في ال ANDROID', '<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;=\"\" display:=\"\" inline=\"\" !important;\"=\"\">Android is a free and open source operating system designed primarily for smart phones and tablets and also can be used for TVs, watches, cars and others. It is based on the Linux Kernel and is currently developed by Google. Android applications can be built using Kotlin to build the code and using XML to create Layouts and design. The used IDEs to create Android applications is Android Studio. Our Android course – Basic Level includes step by step instructions, classroom exercises and discussions for understanding the Android environment and tools, creating Android applications from scratch which contain a lot of rich features those included in the Android Studio like view, resources, intent, multimedia and fragmentation working with SQLite database and designing applications that support different languages and screen size. In order to ensure trainees will achieve these targeted objectives, they are required to prepare a final project which includes SQLite database that store a real life data like super market system, school system…etc.</span>', '<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">الآندرويد Android هو نظام تشغيل مجاني مفتوح المصدر مصمم بشكل أساسي للهواتف الذكية والأجهزة اللوحية، كما يمكن استخدامه في أجهزة التلفزيون والساعات والسيارات وغيرها. يعتمد النظام على نواة لينكس Linux Kernel ويتم تطويره حاليًا بواسطة شركة جوجل Google. تم تصميم الدورة لتمكين المتدربين من إنشاء وبناء مختلف التطبيقات التفاعلية في الأندرويد باستخدام أحدث لغة مبرمجة مدعومة من جوجل ألا وهي لغة كوتلن بالإضافة إلى تمكينهم من استخدام معظم التقنيات لبناء تطبيقات متقدمة مثل Web API, Google Map, Material Design, Firebase. إن بيئة تطوير IDEs لإنشاء تطبيقات الآندرويد Android هي آندرويد استوديو Android Studio.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">يتضمن المستوى الأول من الدورة تعليمات خطوة بخطوة وتمارين عملية ومناقشات لفهم بيئة وأدوات نظام الآندرويد Android، لإنشاء تطبيقات النظام من الصفر باستخدام الميزات والأدوات المضمنة في برنامج اندرويد استوديو</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">Android Studio مثل: ادوات العرض, الموارد, الأهداف والغاية, الوسائط المتعددة, وميزات التجزئة التي تعمل مع قاعدة بيانات SQLite, بالإضافة إلى تصميم التطبيقات التي تدعم لغات مختلفة وحجم الشاشة. ولضمان تحقيق المتدربين لهذه الأهداف السابقة, يتعين عليهم إعداد مشروع نهائي يتضمن قاعدة بيانات SQLite التي تقوم بتخزين بيانات واقعية مثل أنظمة الأسواق, الأنظمة المدرسية, ...الخ.</p>', '<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">Being familiar with the mobile application development architecture.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">Building stand-alone mobile applications which include many features like multimedia, themes, view group and fragmentation.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">Getting the techniques, skills and abilities to build Android applications with different storage techniques like Shared Preferences and SQLite database.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">Supporting different screen sizes, different languages and versions for your mobile app.</p>', '<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">التعرف على بنية تطوير تطبيقات الهاتف المحمول.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">بناء ت