(34, 20, 'FULL STACK IN IOS', 'الدورة الشاملة في ال IOS', '<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;=\"\" display:=\"\" inline=\"\" !important;\"=\"\">The iOS training course is designed for those who want to develop applications for iPhone and iPad in which they will gain the most important skills to design the user interface for iOS applications using Xcode’s GUI tools, including Buttons, Switches, Sliders, PageControllers, and ImageViews, in addition to learn how to secure, tune, package, and deploy iOS applications, build applications that use web services and submit iOS application to the app store.</span><br>', '<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;=\"\" display:=\"\" inline=\"\" !important;\"=\"\">تم تصميم دورة تطوير تطبيقات الاي او اس iOS لأولئك الذين يريدون تعلم كيفية تصميم وإنشاء ونشر تطبيقات الآيفون والآيباد وكذلك يتعلم فيها المشاركون أهم المعلومات والمهارات اللازمة لتصميم واجهة المستخدم UI بطريقة جذابة باستخدام أدوات Xcode’s GUI, بالإضافة الى تعلم كيفية حماية, ضبط ونشر هذه التطبيقات, وكذلك تصميم وانشاء التطبيقات التي تستخدم خدمات الويب.</span><br>', '<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">Introducing participants to iPhone and iPad development, emphasizing the newest technologies and best practices.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">Developing applications for iOS devices.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">Understanding how iOS applications work, their life cycle, settings, and using external resources.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">Designing and developing useful iOS applications with compelling user interfaces by using, extending, and creating your own layouts and Views.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">Building the user interface UI and connecting UI window, UI application and UI application delegate.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">Securing, tuning, packaging, and deploying iOS applications.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">Introducing participants to web services consumption.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">Preparing and submitting an iOS application to the app store.</p>', '<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">تعريف المشاركين بتطوير أجهزة الآيفون والآيباد, مع التركيز على أحدث التقنيات وكذلك أفضل الممارسات.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">تطوير تطبيقات للأجهزة بنظام تشغيل الآي او اس iOS.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">التعرف على كيفية عمل تطبيقات iOS وكذلك دورة حياتها والإعدادات الخاصة بها.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">تصميم وتطوير تطبيقات نظام آيفون iOS مفيدة مع واجهات UI جذابة من خلال إنشاء واستخدام النماذج والتنسيقات الخاصة بالمطور.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">بناء واجهات المستخدم في التطبيقات وضبط نوافذ وتطبيقات واجهة المستخدم, وكذلك تفويض المستخدم.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">حماية, ضبط ونشر تطبيقات الآي او اس iOS.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">تعريف المشاركين على تطوير التطبيقات التي تستخدم خدمات الويب.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">تطوير تطبيقات نظام تشغيل الآيفون iOS ونشرها على متجر التطبيقات.</p>', '1', 30, '1556189649-woman-holding-a-smartphone-3168797_1920.jpg', '200', '50', '<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">Introduction</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">Sketch</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">CocoaPods and Xcode Setup</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">NodeJS (Server-side Setup and Development)</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">Firebase Setup</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">Post Screen Implementation (Xcode)</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">Google Maps APIs Integration</p>', '<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">Introduction</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">Sketch</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">CocoaPods and Xcode Setup</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">NodeJS (Server-side Setup and Development)</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">Firebase Setup</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">Post Screen Implementation (Xcode)</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">Google Maps APIs Integration</p><div><div class=\"row row--component-margin\" style=\"color: rgb(41, 48, 59); font-family: \" open=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 15px;\"=\"\"></div></div><div></div>', '1970-01-01', '1970-01-01', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(35, 20, 'FULL STACK IN JAVA', ' الدورة الشاملة في ال JAVA', '<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">If you are a learning enthusiast and want to create a quick and efficient web application, and you have some Java knowledge and a little or no knowledge about the Java networking programming, then this course is for you. “Full Stack Java developer Practical Guide\" introduces you to Java, JSP, Restful WS, and spring. In this course, you will be able to combine all the ways to connect to the database and learn how to make it in an informative and attractive way. Here, you will learn all the basic concepts, tools, functions, and required topics which usually a Java Developer requires during the web application development process. The course starts with Java, including multi-threading, Lambdas, Collections debugging and introduction to GIT. Then we will move towards JSP and Servlets. Once we are done with JSP and Servlets, we will start exploring Hibernate. An application will be built using JSP and Hibernate as well.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">Java, JSP, and Servlets are core technologies, now once we have completed the core technologies, we will move towards spring framework. Spring framework is among the most popular Java framework, we will cover the spring framework, and then we will start with the very important \"Restful web services\". Finally, after completion for web-services, we will start with spring boot.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">I will start with a brief overview. Then I will show you how to set up your development for Full Stack Java by installing Eclipse on various operating systems along with the following topics.</p>', '<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" fo